item.description:
Hey Everybody,

So I know that it's St. Patrick's day and you probably already have plans, but I will be performing along with my classmates in an improv show at Improv Boston. Our group is called made of plastic and I promise that you'll get a very good laugh from it. I believe tickets are only $5. It would mean a lot if you guys could come out and support. So drink some green ale and come out for a laugh. we're performing in the cabaret space so seating is limited I would try and get there around 8 but we perform at 830, hope to see you there


Keep it Easy!

Seth
item.name: Made of Plastic Featuring Seth starring at Improv Boston
